uls-desc: Baitalasi de hacingga arga be alibufi gisun be sonjoro, gisun -i sindabun be teksilere
ext-uls-undo-language-tooltip-text-local: Ere Uiki -i gisun emgeri halabuhabi. [[Special:GlobalPreferences|Gubci jalan jecen -i adanara ton -i sindabun]] be baicafi, gubci Uiki -i gisun be halakini.
uls-betafeature-desc: Foholon ban -i Gisun -i iletun be iletulere, ese gisun sini gisun de daljingga.
ext-uls-display-settings-desc: Meniyu -i gisun jai hergen -i arbun be sindabure.
ext-uls-language-buttons-help: Meniyu -i gisun be halara. Baktambun -i gisun halaburakū.
ext-uls-display-settings-anon-log-in-cta: [[Special:UserLogin|Oron de dosifi]] meniyu -i gisun be sonjoro.
ext-uls-webfonts-settings-info: Ekiyembuhe hergen be beyei aššame danglotlara, jai ujui sonjoro hergen -i arbun be sonjoro be aljara.
ext-uls-input-disable: Dosimbure agūra hajun be baitalara be nakara
ext-uls-input-disable-info: Dosimbure agūra hajun emgeri baitalara be nakabuhabi.
ext-uls-input-disable-notification: Dosimbure agūra hajun emgeri baitalara be nakabuhabi.
ext-uls-input-disable-notification-info-: Si ai erinde gisun -i sindabun de dosimbure agūra hajun be baitalaci ombi.
Si ai erinde gisun -i iletun -i dalbashūn gisun -i sindabun de dosimbure agūra hajun be baitalaci ombi.
ext-uls-compact-link-info: Gubci gisun (Sini beye jai weri -i sasari sonjoho fukjingga sonjoro hacin deri jihengge)
ext-uls-compact-language-links-preferenc: [[$1|Acamjara gisun -i iletun]] be baitalara, ineku iletun de sinde daljingga gisun be baktambumbi.
ext-uls-compact-no-results: Ere afaha sini suwelehe gisun de alibuhakūngge.
ext-uls-setlang-error: Sini ujui sonjoro gisun be icemlere de ufaracun tucike. Ufaracun: $1
ext-uls-setlang-message: Sini anabuha holboho futa $1 ($2) iletulere jecen dere be baitalara be baibumbi.
ext-uls-setlang-heading: Jecen dere -i gisun be halarao halarakūn?
ext-uls-empty-state-desc: Kemuni baitalaci ojoro gūwa gisun -i ban akū
ext-uls-empty-state-header-actions-avail: Kemuni gūwa gisun akū. Ice gisun be nonggireo?
ext-uls-empty-state-desc-actions-availab: Ineku baktambun de elei labdu gisun -i ban be nonggibure.
